{"tid":2107844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英航母伊利沙伯女王號擬部署亞洲以製衡中國","createTime":"2020-07-14T06:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T10:04:48.000Z","uid":51665,"like":105,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"82469bd14366d4d3e16be48f7329d3a6d7892a82","tid":2107844,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:52:55.000Z","msg":"造價31億英鎊的伊利沙伯女王號，據報將在亞洲地區與美國、日本盟友展開軍演。（泰晤士報）<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士報》引述消息指，英國軍方正計劃把新航母伊利沙伯女王號部署在亞洲地區，以對抗中國日益增加的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，伊利沙伯女王號將在明年初首次作為航母戰鬥群的主力，展開處女航行。造價31億英鎊（約54.2億新元）的伊利沙伯女王號，料將在亞洲地區與美國、日本盟友展開軍演。期間也會作為&ldquo;浮動的交易會場&rdquo;，為討論協議提供平台。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，伊麗莎白女王號在2014年7月4日下水，2017年12月7日正式服役。該航母為常規動力，計劃搭載24-36架F-35B戰機和14架直升機。<br />\n<br />\n伊莉莎白女王號和它的姊妹艦威爾士親王號是英國皇家海軍有史以來建造的最大的艦艇。它們的目的是多用途的載體，可適應完成多種角色。兩艘航母的母港都是樸次茅斯海軍基地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202007/20200714/_methode_times_prod_web_bin_d9bbf9c0-c549-11ea-b1ec-faab6f383ba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com.sg%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle_large_full%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F202007%2F20200714%2F_methode_times_prod_web_bin_d9bbf9c0-c549-11ea-b1ec-faab6f383ba1.jpg&h=23c8bcf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=zh-TW&amp;sl=zh-CN&amp;u=https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20200714-1069049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.google.com%2Ftranslate%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW%26sl%3Dzh-CN%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2Fstory20200714-1069049&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=7a9eb2d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=zh-TW&amp;sl=zh-CN&amp;u=https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20200714-1069049</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5498a3e3494aee9b5b2f2c7ae422f2a4714714b3","tid":2107844,"uid":38904,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"百國聯軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf4141f7559837ce9644748b0ad9daee1f61282","tid":2107844,"uid":51665,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:56:54.000Z","msg":"隻艦又細個樣又柒點夠我國遼寧號fight呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/16367/production/_96838909_5f4cf063-1bb3-4dd8-a123-ff1a84f7e1fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F976%2Fcpsprodpb%2F16367%2Fproduction%2F_96838909_5f4cf063-1bb3-4dd8-a123-ff1a84f7e1fa.jpg&h=c1841bb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3fdbba188ec26d395c26baafa23219011d8de37","tid":2107844,"uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"點解唔用黎對付俄？"},{"pid":"1c6c1c23b49eccd6256b97f00550fd3ebf1ef5ed","tid":2107844,"uid":30084,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"核動力?可以去邊到補給?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台灣日本?"},{"pid":"aa071bd2e216e2e78cfa1c5776e5cd8cca21fb32","tid":2107844,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cf4141f7559837ce9644748b0ad9daee1f61282","tid":2107844,"uid":51665,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:56:54.000Z","msg":"隻艦又細個樣又柒點夠我國遼寧號fight呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/16367/production/_96838909_5f4cf063-1bb3-4dd8-a123-ff1a84f7e1fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F976%2Fcpsprodpb%2F16367%2Fproduction%2F_96838909_5f4cf063-1bb3-4dd8-a123-ff1a84f7e1fa.jpg&h=c1841bb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:59:07.000Z","msg":"好型"},{"pid":"6b864c73e1c7f5dfc1fe82914c95ccfb304fcc3a","tid":21